    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Areas or facilities designed or used primarily for shooting guns at targets, whether for sport or as training. Typically the area includes various ranges or distances marked off between the respective firing points and the targets.</Note_Text>
